data.description: This home on a corner lot, in an established SW neighborhood is move in ready.  The home features 3 bedroom and 1 1/2 baths with plenty of closet space.  There are 3 living areas that offer flexibility for both living and entertaining.  The eat-in kitchen would make any cook delighted with the gas range, counter space, under cabinet lighting and abundance of storage.  The laundry room is directly off the kitchen and features plenty of additional storage.  There is an attached car port and a single car garage on the side of the house with also room to park and RV or boat.
